name: أوليفر براون
ratings:
(4⭐) Everything is good. The best café in Othaim Mall 😍. Recommended 👍 - 4 years ago | (1⭐) VERY BAD CUSTOMER SERVICE

Everyday I visit Oliver Brown cafe, usually during the after noon, the employees there are very welcoming during this time.

Today, I went to the cafe in the morning at about 10 am, it was closed and no one was there knowing that it usually opens about 8 to 9 am. I waited for about one hour and no one came. I went to a near coffee shop and I bought coffee.

After about half an hour the employee came, and she starting saying that we cannot drink our coffee there. So I ordered from her 2 cups  but she was very rude and she treated us very badly. She was insisting on us to buy desert from her otherwise we cannot stay. Also she said that we had to stay at the cafe from where we bought the coffee from, so we left.

Unfortunatly, it is my last time for me visiting this cafe.

I was extremely disappointed with this experience and the way that we got treated.

I strongly advise to seek for another cafe nearby to have a pleasant and enjoyable experience.

Its truly a shame that such a beuitiful space is marred by such a customer service experience. - a year ago | (2⭐) I love their mugs , actually bought 2 to add to my collection. ( 2 stars for the coffee mugs)
The coffee was ok.. nothing special
Just another mall coffee shop..

I don’t think I will last due to the competition in serving coffee in the mall - 6 years ago | (1⭐) We ordered cappuccino, mojito, and pink chocolate milkshake and cake. The cappuccino is inedible, the cake is oily. It’s not made with milk, it’s made with water!! They got our order wrong and served us the wrong drinks. I could not finish my milkshake as it was way too sweet. They did not have any diet sugar unlike all other cafés we have been to in Riyadh. My aunt was very disappointed and could not have anything to drink because she is diabetic. The food was unpleasant and very oily, especially the English cake. Overall, it was a very disappointing and unpleasant experience that was a complete shock to our expectations.

If I could give 0 stars, I would. - a year ago | (5⭐) This coconut hot chocolate is DELICIOUS!!!!!! I Highly recommend everyone to try this, it is so rich yet coconuty. - 2 years ago
